        <abstract> 
<p>Asks what his profits on the reprints of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> will be when half have been sold.</p>  
<p>Good reviews in <hi rend="italic">Saturday Review</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Pall Mall Gazette</hi>;</p>  
<p>contemptuous one as usual in <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi>.</p> 
